newsitem.title: USA: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,075 contracts.
newsitem.headline: CBOT overnight Project A ag volume 1,075 contracts.

text.p: The Chicago Board of Trade Project A overnight agricultural trading volume totalled 1,075 contracts compared with 946 overnight Tuesday, according to the CBOT.
There were 46 wheat, 182 corn, 705 soybean, 41 soymeal, 74 soyoil, five corn calls, 10 corn puts and 12 soybean calls traded.
In overnight trading, wheat was one to two cents higher, corn was steady to 1/2 cent higher and soybeans were four to five cents higher.
